      "name": "Seasonal shape",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "markdown",
          "text": "## Seasonal shape\n\nRidership roughly triples from the depths of winter to the peak of fall. The\nweekly rhythm is a commuter's: weekday volume is carried by registered members,\nwhile casual demand swells on warm weekends."
        },
