      "name": "Outlook",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "markdown",
          "text": "## Outlook\n\nTwo levers move the number: **weather** (outside our control, but forecastable)\nand **membership growth** (the compounding 2011→2012 trend). Sustaining\ndouble-digit growth means converting the weekend casual rider into a weekday\nregistered one — the segment with the steadiest, highest-value demand."
        }
